
Homework #2 - Vijoy Sunil Kumar
CSCI4229/5229 Summer 2018

3-D Scene Rendering

Key bindings:
 *  1	       Render room
 *  2          Render tables
 *  3          Render lamp
 *  4          Render chairs
 *  5          Render ALL
 *  6          Render OFF
 *  m          Toggle orthogonal/perspective/first person
 *  a          Toggle axes
 *  arrows     Change view angle
 *  PgDn/PgUp  Zoom in and out
 *  0          Reset 
 *  .          View center of scene
 *  ESC        Exit
